          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2019-04-11T18:18:52Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Contingency Operation Waste and Fraud Prevention Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Defense (DOD) to submit to Congress a strategy to prevent corruption in any reconstruction efforts associated with a military operation. It also establishes the position of Senior Anticorruption Officer in DOD, the Department of State, and the U.S. Agency for International Development, and a Working Group for Anticorruption.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-06-27T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
